props is being able to pass data into components and then use that data in there.

concept of configuring components is called props.

prop accept all value types

in react commponent function, it is pretty much the same with js but, only accept one parameter which typically called props, but we can name it as we want.

props are custom html attributes set on components.
react merge all props into a single object.
props are passed to the commponent function as the first argument by react.